        "timestamp": "2019-09-19 10:27:37.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nI've tried to add characterization tests for the problematic changes introduced to PnfEventReadyDmaapClient in https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/so/+/86267\n\nBesides the current issue: https://jira.onap.org/browse/SO-2349 and the earlier issue fixed by Lukasz: https://jira.onap.org/browse/SO-2289\nthere are at least two other issues suggesting changes introduced to PnfEventReadyDmaapClient in https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/so/+/86267 are completely broken / never taken into use (please see my other comments in this review)\n\nSo unless there is a good reason to keep those changes from https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/so/+/86267 I'd suggest removing/reverting them.\n\n@Seshu, @Marios please comment",
